Installation:
-------------
sudo apt install i3 i3blocks i3lock xorg     # i3 base
sudo apt install xfce4-terminal curl         # basic terminal setup
sudo apt install sxiv feh                    # image viewer & background display control
sudo apt install xfce4-notifyd               # notification service
sudo apt install arandr
sudo apt install network-manager             # network service manager
sudo apt install xfce4-powermanager acpi     # for laptop power management
sudo apt install pulseaudio pulseaudio-utils # audio support
sudo apt install pavucontrol                 # audio control
sudo apt install scrot imagemagick xautolock # screen lock
sudo apt install thunar or nautilus          # file manager
sudo apt install zsh neovim git bat geany    # developer tools
sudo apt install firefox                     # browser
sudo apt install gdebi htop                  # operations tools

Install whatever login display manager:
---------------------------------------
sudo apt install slim (does not need any dependency)

Additionally:
-------------
enable screen lock script:
-------------------------
chmod +x ~/.config/i3/scripts/lock

virtual machine? Install these additional packages to have a better experience:
-------------------------------------------------------------------------------
sudo apt-install virtualbox-dkms virtualbox-guest-dkms virtualbox-guest-x11

install docker (https://docs.docker.com/engine/install/ubuntu/) & enable use without sudo:
-----------------------------------------------------------------------------------------
sudo usermod -aG docker ${USER}               # logout and logon or run su - ${USER}

# easy run
sudo apt install i3 i3blocks i3lock xorg \
    xfce4-terminal curl \
    sxiv feh \
    xfce4-notifyd \
    arandr \
    network-manager \
    xfce4-powermanager acpi \
    pulseaudio pulseaudio-utils \
    pavucontrol \
    scrot imagemagick xautolock \
    thunar or nautilus \
    zsh neovim git bat geany \
    firefox \
    gdebi htop
